### Context

This is ResNext50_32x4d predictions on the training data of the 2020 Cassava Leaf Disease Classification challenge (as produced by this notebook: https://www.kaggle.com/bjoernholzhauer/cassava-leaf-disease-classif-eda-cv-strategy). 


### Content

The predictions.npy file contains one row per image in the training data and one column per 1000 ImageNet categories.
